#text=I love to save money everywhere I can , a penny saved a penny earned kind of philosophy .
#text=So when I analyzed our finances I saw we could save a considerable amount of money by doing more grocery shopping .
#text=I set up our strategy to go every weekend and budget about 200 dollars for the two of us each week .
#text=We will start off buying produce , fruits and vegetables and such .
#text=Then we move over and look for the best deals on meat .
#text=We usually get fish , beef , chicken and pork .
#text=Next we 'll head over towards dairy and eggs .
#text=I like to get the 18 packs of eggs .
#text=They are protein loaded and super cheap .
#text=I 'll pick up some cottage cheese and about 4 to 6 pounds of cheese .
#text=We then get a couple of things out of the frozen section .
